request.description:
Returns feedback data for graphing personal feedback vs peer feedback over time.

**Response:**
```json
{
  "message": "Feedback graph data fetched successfully",
  "data": {
    "sportId": "64abc123...",
    "sessionType": "Skill Practice",
    "timeFilter": "7D",
    "summary": {
      "totalSessions": 7,
      "personalFeedback": { "count": 7, "average": 6.5, "best": 10 },
      "peerFeedback": { "count": 5, "average": 7.0, "best": 10 }
    },
    "dataPoints": [
      {
        "date": "2026-01-01T...",
        "dateFormatted": "Wed, 1 Nov",
        "personalFeedback": 2,
        "peerFeedback": 0,
        "peerFeedbackCount": 0,
        "details": {
          "matchType": "Competition",
          "matchResult": "Win",
          "duration": "3:15",
          "notes": "Great session",
          "hasMedia": true
        }
      }
    ]
  }
}
```

Returns skill training breakdown by category for pie chart visualization.

**Response:**
```json
{
  "message": "Skill training graph data fetched successfully",
  "data": {
    "sportId": "64abc123...",
    "giNoGi": "All",
    "timeFilter": "all",
    "summary": {
      "totalSessions": 100,
      "classCount": 12,
      "manualLogCount": 10,
      "categoryCount": 7
    },
    "categories": [
      {
        "_id": "cat1",
        "name": "Takedowns",
        "count": 20,
        "percentage": 20,
        "skills": [
          { "_id": "skill1", "name": "Single Leg Takedown", "count": 8 },
          { "_id": "skill2", "name": "Double Leg Takedown", "count": 6 }
        ]
      }
    ]
  }
}
```

Returns the actual number of training sessions attended by the authenticated user in a specific month at their gym. User is automatically identified from the auth token.

**Response:**
```json
{
  "message": "Monthly training count fetched",
  "data": {
    "count": 8,
    "month": "january",
    "year": 2026
  }
}
```
